<span id="freeTextContainer3588349216539548119">Love all the stories. Reading them to my kids and then asking them the morals as they see it. I know they don&apos;t understand it all but I hope it plants a seed in them to be kinder, empathetic people and not letting others abuse this kindness. Lots of witty and self evaluation stories told in animal form. Short and sweet with lots of wisdom and mental strength. </span>
